'''Real Alternative'''是一個用於[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]作業系統的[[編解碼器|編解碼器]]安裝包，由[[KL_Software|KL Software]]開發，使用了開源視訊濾光器[[Real_Media_Splitter|Real Media Splitter]]及RealMedia[[視訊编解码器|視訊编解码器]]。該編解碼器可在沒有安裝[[RealPlayer|RealPlayer]]的情況下播放[[RealMedia|RealMedia]]檔案，且可用於任何使用[[DirectShow|DirectShow]]的媒體播放器，如包含在安裝包內的[[Media_Player_Classic|Media Player Classic]]。

Real Alternative與許多免費的編解碼器安裝包同梱。由於RealPlayer令用戶感到不滿，因此有些人較為喜歡使用Real Alternative。<ref>{{cite web 
| url = http://cws.internet.com/article/2684-3933.htm 
| title = Real Alternative: Better Than the Real Thing? 
| author = Adam Stone 
| publisher = [[Jupitermedia|Jupitermedia]] Corporation 
| work = WinPlanet Reviews 
| accessdate = 2006年8月22日 
| archive-date = 2006年9月4日 
| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20060904074252/http://cws.internet.com/article/2684-3933.htm 
| dead-url = no 
}}</ref>

== 合法性 ==
據[[RealNetworks|RealNetworks]]表示該編解碼器安裝包並不合法，由於RealNetworks擁有[[RealMedia|RealMedia]]編解碼器的版權，而RealNetworks並沒有授權KL Software使用其編解碼器。<ref>{{cite web
| author = Karl Lillevold, RealNetworks
| date = 2005年12日1日
| url = http://forum.doom9.org/showthread.php?threadid=68399
| title = RealPlayer 10.5, installation, performance, etc.
| publisher = [[Doom9|Doom9]]
| accessdate = 2006年8月22日
| archive-date = 2012年3月21日
| archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/66K6rGxYH?url=http://forum.doom9.org/showthread.php?threadid=68399
| dead-url = yes
}}</ref> 

2010年，RealNetworks起訴了26歲的荷蘭網站管理員Hilbrand Edskes非法地在他自己的網站上提供了Real Alternative編解碼器的超連結，並聲稱Real Alternative是反向工程編解碼器。<ref>{{cite news |last=De Winter |first=Brenno |title=RealNetworks crushes Dutch webmaster for hyperlink |url=http://www.pcadvisor.co.uk/news/tech-industry/3299285/realnetworks-crushes-dutch-webmaster-for-hyperlink/ |accessdate=August 29, 2011 |newspaper=PC Advisor |publisher=[[International_Data_Group|IDG]] |date=August 25, 2011 |archive-date=2015-05-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150502185000/http://www.pcadvisor.co.uk/news/tech-industry/3299285/realnetworks-crushes-dutch-webmaster-for-hyperlink/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>2011年11月，RealNetworks對Edskes的訴訟被駁回，RealNetworks因而被判向他賠償48,000歐元，但此案件使Edskes已損失了66,000歐元的律師費。<ref>{{cite news|last=de Winter|first=Brenno|title=RealNetworks gaat door met rechtszaak om hyperlink|url=http://webwereld.nl/nieuws/108474/realnetworks-gaat-door-met-rechtszaak-om-hyperlink.html|newspaper=WebWerld (Dutch language)|date=November 7, 2011|dead-url=yes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121116055148/http://webwereld.nl/nieuws/108474/realnetworks-gaat-door-met-rechtszaak-om-hyperlink.html|archive-date=2012-11-16|access-date=2020-03-29}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Collin|first=Branko|title=Internet thugs Realnetworks lose case against Hilbrand Edskes|url=http://www.24oranges.nl/2011/11/06/internet-thugs-realnetworks-lose-case-against-hilbrand-edskes/|accessdate=December 9, 2011|newspaper=24Oranges|date=November 6, 2011|archive-date=2020-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806173705/http://www.24oranges.nl/2011/11/06/internet-thugs-realnetworks-lose-case-against-hilbrand-edskes/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==功能限制==
Real Alternative功能上有所限制，例如不能播放RealVideo 10與RealAudio 5.0等較新的RealMedia檔案，{{code|.smi}}及{{code|.smil}}檔案只能播放片段的第一部份，除了[[Media_Player_Classic|Media Player Classic]]外，[[RealTime_Stream_Protocol|RealTime Stream Protocol]]（rtsp://）不能於其他DirectShow媒體放器中播放。{{Dead link|date=2020年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}<ref name="limit">Limitations to Real Alternative{{cite web |url=http://www.codecguide.com/about_real.htm |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2006-12-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://swap.stanford.edu/20090620234430/http://www.codecguide.com/about_real.htm |archivedate=2009-06-20 }}</ref>

